T</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-joint-exercises-held-with-us-s-china-sea-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲黄金印度转向溢价，农历新年引发其他中心的买盘</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-india-flips-premium-lunar-new-year-sparks-buying-other-hubs-2024-02-09/</link><description>印度实物黄金交易商本周四个月来首次收取溢价，原因是当地价格下跌，购买量增加，而即将到来的农历新年提振了中国和其他地区的黄金活动。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 11:12:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-india-flips-premium-lunar-new-year-sparks-buying-other-hubs-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘出价：华尔街保持创纪录水平，关注通胀修正</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-09/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 11:03:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>资生堂利润下滑，中国消费者低迷又成为受害者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-consumer-slump-claims-another-victim-shiseido-profit-slides-2024-02-09/</link><description>周五，资生堂成为中国经济放缓的最新受害者，这家日本化妆品制造商的年收益下滑了 40%，这对许多全球消费品公司的盈利造成了打击。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 08:45:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-consumer-slump-claims-another-victim-shiseido-profit-slides-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>政策支持下1月份银行新增贷款创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-january-new-bank-loans-hit-record-high-policy-support-2024-02-09/</link><description>随着央行采取行动提振陷入困境的经济，中国一月份新增银行贷款增幅超出预期，创历史新高，强化了未来几个月出台更多刺激措施的预期。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 08:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-january-new-bank-loans-hit-record-high-policy-support-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>梅西在中国的影响力越来越大，杭州队取消了阿根廷友谊赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/hong-kong-organiser-partly-refund-inter-miami-tickets-after-messi-backlash-2024-02-09/</link><description>由于莱昂内尔·梅西上周未能参加国际迈阿密在香港举行的比赛，中国体育当局取消了下个月阿根廷和尼日利亚之间的国际友谊赛。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 07:44:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/hong-kong-organiser-partly-refund-inter-miami-tickets-after-messi-backlash-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>爱马仕销售额超过奢侈品竞争对手，股价创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hermes-sales-jump-175-demand-expensive-goods-persists-2024-02-09/</link><description>爱马仕表示，由于其销量将在 2023 年底超过奢侈品竞争对手，因此将进一步提高价格，从而帮助这家柏金包制造商的股价升至历史新高。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 07:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hermes-sales-jump-175-demand-expensive-goods-persists-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>普京对战争与和平、第三次世界大战和人工智能说了些什么？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/what-did-putin-say-war-peace-ww3-ai-2024-02-09/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在周五发表的采访中谈到了乌克兰的战争与和平、遗传学和人工智能进步的风险以及对世界大战的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 07:04:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/what-did-putin-say-war-peace-ww3-ai-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国经济困境加剧，投资银行准备迎接更多亚洲裁员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-woes-mount-investment-banks-brace-more-asia-job-cuts-2024-02-09/</link><description>猎头公司和银行家表示，尽管日本和印度的交易前景光明，但由于中国经济和市场动荡加剧，收入压力加大，亚洲西方投行今年的裁员预计将增加。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 07:01:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-woes-mount-investment-banks-brace-more-asia-job-cuts-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>百度与联想达成第三笔中国人工智能智能手机交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-partners-with-lenovo-third-china-ai-smartphone-deal-2024-02-09/</link><description>中国的百度与联想合作，将其生成式人工智能（AI）技术应用到联想的智能手机上，这是与手机制造商的最新合作，旨在为其人工智能模型寻求实际应用。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 05:48:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-partners-with-lenovo-third-china-ai-smartphone-deal-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：杜克能源将把中国电池巨头宁德时代从海军陆战队基地撤出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/duke-energy-remove-chinese-battery-giant-catl-marine-corps-base-2024-02-09/</link><description>美国公用事业公司杜克能源向路透社证实，在国会的压力下，该公司计划退役中国电池制造商宁德时代在美国最大的海军陆战队基地之一生产的储能电池，并将在其民用项目中逐步淘汰宁德时代的产品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 05:05:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/duke-energy-remove-chinese-battery-giant-catl-marine-corps-base-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>美元坚挺令金价承压，交易员寻求美联储线索，收益率走高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-flat-safe-haven-demand-offsets-us-dollar-strength-2024-02-09/</link><description>受美元走强和国债收益率上升的影响，周五金价走低，而投资者则期待下周的美国通胀数据，以寻找美联储何时开始降息的线索。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 04:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-flat-safe-haven-demand-offsets-us-dollar-strength-2024-02-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>